                <mxCell id="jz4z2MhY_K-bpB4hze0K-16" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Landing Page&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Rubics is in Three component, rotate slowly counterclockwise horizontally.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If time allows:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- The scramble effect of Rubics&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Controls on click on Rubics&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Resolve cubics animation&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Loop&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
