                <mxCell id="jz4z2MhY_K-bpB4hze0K-23" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;So, you are xxx&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;# Placeholder text to showcase some instructions to help the user increase their performance to solve Rubics Cube&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;# Text keep rendering in a TPS that is controlled and length controlled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
