                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="jz4z2MhY_K-bpB4hze0K-31" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;If non beginner&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Controls:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;- Mouse clicks on sides&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;- Keyboard mapping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;- Timer, starts on clicks or keyboard first press&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;Button&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;- Give up button&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;- Then the rubics solve itself&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;Good to have:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;&gt;- A solver sequence formula on the side, opacity low&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
